  <name>Candy Wrapper</name>
  <summary>Screen-wrapping arcade action</summary>

  <developer id="net.hhoney">
    <name translatable="no">HHoney Software</name>
  </developer>

  <description>
    <p>Play your way through 20 levels of this arcade screen-wrapping action game inspired by Bubble Bobble!</p>
    <p>Controls: Arrows + Spacebar / WASD / IJKL</p>
    <p>Candy Wrapper was originally made within 24 hours for the 100 Lines of Code GameMaker Jam.</p>
  </description>

